OL,3,CReports over hitting and smacking of
OL,4,Cchildren triple in a year, NSPCC says
OL,6,FThe NSPCC said more than half of the
OL,7,Ftotal contacts to its helpline
OL,8,Fregarding physical punishment were
OL,9,Ffrom members of the public who were
OL,10,Fconcerned about a parent's behaviour.
OL,12,FNSPCC chief executive Sir Peter
OL,13,FWanless described the rise as "hugely
OL,14,Fconcerning".
OL,16,FHe said: "Mounting evidence shows that
OL,17,Fphysically disciplining children can
OL,18,Fbe damaging and counter-productive.
