OL,3,CReports over hitting and smacking of
OL,4,Cchildren triple in a year, NSPCC says
OL,6,F"A long overdue change in the law to
OL,7,Fprevent physical punishment of
OL,8,Fchildren must be delivered by our
OL,9,Fpolitical leaders," he added.
OL,11,FWales made any type of corporal
OL,12,Fpunishment - including smacking,
OL,13,Fhitting, slapping and shaking -
OL,14,Fillegal in March 2022, while Scotland
OL,15,Fintroduced a similar ban in November
OL,16,F2020.
