OL,3,CReports over hitting and smacking of
OL,4,Cchildren triple in a year, NSPCC says
OL,6,FEarlier this year, the Royal College
OL,7,Fof Paediatrics and Child Health
OL,8,F(RCPCH) called for a UK-wide ban on
OL,9,Fsmacking, saying the current law in
OL,10,FEngland and Northern Ireland has
OL,11,Fcreated "grey areas" which mean there
OL,12,Fis sometimes a defence to physical
OL,13,Fpunishment.
