OL,3,CReports over hitting and smacking of
OL,4,Cchildren triple in a year, NSPCC says
OL,6,FRCPCH officer for child protection and
OL,7,Fconsultant paediatrician Professor
OL,8,FAndrew Rowland said the NSPCC data
OL,9,F"must be a further wake-up call of the
OL,10,Fneed for change".
OL,12,FHe added: "As a UK-based
OL,13,Fpaediatrician, I think it is wholly
OL,14,Fwrong that children in England and
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland have less protection
OL,16,Fand less protection of their rights
OL,17,Fthan their Scottish and Welsh
OL,18,Fcounterparts.
