OL,3,CReports over hitting and smacking of
OL,4,Cchildren triple in a year, NSPCC says
OL,6,F"It is time to outlaw physical
OL,7,Fpunishment across the whole of the UK
OL,8,Fand finally put an end to this
OL,9,Foutdated practice."
OL,11,FIn 2022, then-opposition leader Sir
OL,12,FKeir Starmer called on other areas of
OL,13,Fthe UK to follow Wales in banning the
OL,14,Fsmacking of children.
OL,16,FSpeaking at the time, he said: "What
OL,17,Fit (the ban) does is give children the
OL,18,Fprotection that adults already have,
OL,19,Fand that is the right thing."
